name: Rambut Hitam by Rica Ojara Manzana 2023

metadata.name: Rambut Hitam by Rica Ojara Manzana 2023
metadata.description:
This is Rica Ojara Manzana, Contemporary artist at Tokyo.
My art works, very minimal, just put in the cookie tin, something. This time, I put on my black long hair, early life. Perhaps 35 years old. I had very beautiful hair at young time. Also, I was very proud of my black, shiny hair, that every day with the wind. Passed long time, and never back again. 

This art works the original appraisal agency "Happy Nyaan" proves that it is genuine.
